Photo by Yup That Exists on August 28, 2021. May be an illustration of text that says 'YUP Yup That Exists @yup.that.exists Restoration reveals hidden Vermeer painting of a young Cupid hanging in the background of a painting.'.

node.text:
After X-rays were done on a 17th-century painting by the Dutch artist Johannes Vermeer, it was discovered that there was something being covered up on the wall in the background. When the painting was restored, it revealed that Vermeer in fact had painted an image of a young naked cupid in the background. So even 346, Vermeer is still technically releasing new paintings! 

Follow @yup.that.exists

Photo by Yup That Exists on August 22, 2021. May be an image of one or more people, outdoors and text that says 'YUP Yup That Exists @yup.that.exists Pakistani students plant over 50,000 trees in 40 seconds in order to set a new world record.'.

node.text:
Last week 12,500 students from city of Gujranwala, Pakistan, came together to break the "most trees planted in a minute" record. They ended up smashing the old record of 37,000, with an astonishing 52,000 trees! If we all tried to break this record every now and then we might not be f*cked 100 years from now 😕. 

Credit: @plant4pak 

Follow us @yup.that.exists

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Yup That Exists on August 21, 2021. May be an image of outdoors and text that says 'YUP Yup That Exists @yup.that.exists China has been building a "wall of bees" on the side of mountain since the year 100 AD, which now houses 700 colonies.'.

node.text:
On the side of a mountain in Shennongjia National Nature Reserve, China, lies a giant wall of bees. Since the 2nd century AD, locals have been transfering hives 4,000 feet above sea level, to this rural mountainside. Although this altitude is not common for bees, they are safe from predators and other hazards, such as pesticides here. 

Follow @yup.that.exists

node.text:
The Tesla Bot, a prototype that is set to be available next year, was officially announced yesterday by Elon Musk. The robot is designed to eliminate “dangerous, repetitive and boring tasks,” like bending over to pick something up, or going to the grocery store, Musk said. “Essentially, in the future, physical work will be a choice.”

node.text:
The Great Green Wall or Great Green Wall of the Sahara and the Sahel is a project led by the African Union, initially conceived as a way to combat desertification in the Sahel region and hold back expansion of the Sahara, by planting a wall of trees stretching across the entire Sahel. 

Follow @yup.that.exists
